      "name": "COU1 operating envelope: flow rate, speed, and geometry tolerance bounds",
      "description": "Validated operating envelope: pump flow rate 2.0–6.0 L/min; rotational speed 1500–3500 RPM; inlet pressure 5–15 mmHg; outlet pressure 60–120 mmHg; impeller tip clearance 0.15–0.35 mm (±0.10 mm manufacturing tolerance); blood temperature 35–37°C. All five evaluated flow-speed operating points fall within these bounds."
    }
